snippet: The strains on Jeffrey D. Klein and Dean G. Skelos, a Democrat and Republican who are sharing the leadership of the chamber, are already evident.
abstract: Michael Powell Gotham column on New York State Senators Jeffrey D Klein and Dean G Skelos, Democrat and Republican who are sharing leadership of the chamber in one of Albany's stranger political alliances.
lead_paragraph: The strains on Jeffrey D. Klein and Dean G. Skelos, a Democrat and Republican who are sharing the leadership of the chamber, are already evident.
